	Provided you don't have anything on IRQ 2 or 9, you might 
want to go ahead and run the thing on IRQ 9.  I do.  Here's the 
relevant CONFIG.SYS line for my system:

BASEDEV=SONY31A.ADD /A:0 /P:0340 /I:9

